This book is meant to be a primer both for players to learn a little about the other side of the fence, and to help Storytellers find ways to use  these things in their chronicles.  Usually the chapters have the general material in the front, with the Storyteller section following. Storyteller sections have advisories on  how to use the material, story seeds and potential resources for further information.

