## STARGAZERS

Antonine Teardrop may hold the key to Garou victory against the evil of Eastern Europe,but his tribe's withdrawal from the Garou Nation may have damaged his credibility beyond repair. Even if it has not, servants of the Wyrm want him dead.

## BONEGNAWERS

Valiant Garou warriors return to Eastern Europe to eradicate the growing evil that has confounded their efforts thus far.Where the mighty and noble have failed,hope now rests with humble werewolves who make their homes in filth.

